<h1 id="about">21st International Workshop on
Mining and Learning with Graphs</h1>

<center><em>9th September (2024), Vilnius, jointly with <a href="https://2024.ecmlpkdd.org/" target=_blank>ECMLPKDD2024</a></em></center> <br />

